{"tid":2422110,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"陳茂波：80億維穩費絕非軍費 切勿誤會 這是19年社會件事後的代價","createTime":"2021-02-25T03:27:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-25T12:22:58.000Z","uid":21470,"like":2,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"216dbcd0e603aa75772b100f6b281aa507a643c8","tid":2422110,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T03:27:37.000Z","msg":"陳茂波稱維護國安開支非軍費 預留80億未來數年使用<br />\n<br />\n新一份財政預算案，預算80億元撥款，用作維護國家安全開支。有聽眾致電聯合電台節目，指香港一直是安全的城市，形容撥款是用作「軍費」，認為在現時的環境下，應將資源作為市民救急。<br />\n<br />\n出席節目的財政司司長陳茂波回應說，國安開支絕對不是軍費，希望公眾切勿誤會，又指2019年社會暴力衝突事件，曝露香港在國家安全方面的空隙，有需要預留80億元未來幾年使用。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1577418-20210225.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1577418-20210225.htm&d=L6ZqOc%2BI4Gry4yTyS7cXFfUbXA8pdDK36CymbYVYMuw%3D&h=ed0175b9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1577418-20210225.htm&h=8d02c857\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1577418-20210225.htm</a>"},{"pid":"611cc0f1f5eec87f19c676ced6306f2687a56e19","tid":2422110,"uid":183758,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T03:29:07.000Z","msg":"含撚啦<br />\n<br />\n仲留喺度交稅養支共正傻仔"},{"pid":"a8f943c1e300ec76d59c729353baf5432fb1be6f","tid":2422110,"uid":225798,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T03:29:11.000Z","msg":"不如比英國養航母"},{"pid":"77502873e5b2cc2483e3f9e85a15c9ddfd771588","tid":2422110,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T03:29:38.000Z","msg":"無錢推全民失業援助金 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16cc1c27665a356ce861ff5ab0f8108d9e601066","tid":2422110,"uid":224066,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedB